g=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1810\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-01.jpg\" alt=\"A modern hotel room with earth tones, natural materials, and a built-in bathtub.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-01.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-01-940x945.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-01-800x804.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-01-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-01-768x772.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-01-1528x1536.jpg 1528w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThey chose a single off-white colour to blend the boundaries of walls, floors, and ceilings, erasing joints between corners of the rooms by curving the ends of the wall at the floor and ceiling. There are no sharp shadows around the edge of the spaces.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"2410\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-02.jpg\" alt=\"A modern hotel room with earth tones, natural materials, and a built-in bathtub.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-02.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-02-940x1259.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-02-800x1071.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-02-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-02-1147x1536.jpg 1147w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-02-1530x2048.jpg 1530w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe layouts open the interiors outside towards the East, with each bed positioned to face the view. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"2110\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-03.jpg\" alt=\"A modern hotel room with earth tones and natural materials.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-03.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-03-940x1102.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-03-800x938.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-03-768x900.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-03-1310x1536.jpg 1310w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-03-1747x2048.jpg 1747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAnother important composition is the location of standalone bathtubs, positioned in such a way that it makes it easy to see the scenery.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1810\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-04.jpg\" alt=\"A modern hotel room with earth tones, natural materials, and a built-in bathtub.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-04.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-04-940x945.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-04-800x804.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-04-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-04-768x772.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-villa-room-neutral-tones-051124-1233-04-1528x1536.jpg 1528w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThroughout the rooms, the designers created every piece of oak wood furniture with curves.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-01.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with earth tones and natural materials.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-01.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn one of the bathrooms, there’s a free-standing circular bathroom wall is built with rounded corners clad in small pieces of white marble on both sides. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"2410\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-02.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with earth tones and a curved marble clad shower wall.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-02.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-02-940x1259.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-02-800x1071.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-02-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-02-1147x1536.jpg 1147w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-02-1530x2048.jpg 1530w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe designers decided upon the bright earth tone colours for all fabrics used in the room, together with a final touch of pink, drawing inspiration from the colour of Khao Yai’s soil.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-03.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with earth tones and a curved marble clad shower wall.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-03.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-03-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-03-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-wood-neutral-tones-bathroom-051124-1234-03-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by W Workspace\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
